name: Feed the Beast
description:
Another visual orgy of human dumb-f*ckery. The ‘beast’ is humanity, capitalism, inequality, and greed. Constantly taking resources from the Earth, the oceans and from the animal kingdom, and all for our own benefit. We continue to force feed the insatiable desires of our greedy egos, without a thought to the impact it has on the world we live in.


By @dehiscenceart 2021, 4200px X 6600 px
